th_difficulty_save_current_development = {
	set_country_flag = th_difficulty_saved_current_development
	export_to_variable = {
		which = th_difficulty_current_development
		value = trigger_value:total_development
	}
}

th_difficulty_set_global_variable = {
	1 = {
		set_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_current_highest_dev
			value = 0
		}
	}
}

th_difficulty_set_highest_player_dev_variable = {
	1 = {
		change_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_current_highest_dev
			which = th_difficulty_current_development
		}
	}
	set_global_flag = th_difficulty_dev_up_to_date
}

th_difficulty_setup_counter_variable = {
	1 = {
		set_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_count_development_for_passive
			value = 0
		}
		set_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_count_development_for_agressive
			value = 0
		}
		change_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_count_development_for_passive
			which = th_difficulty_current_highest_dev
		}
		change_variable = {
			which = th_difficulty_count_development_for_agressive
			which = th_difficulty_current_highest_dev
		}
	}
}

add_th_diffuculty_agressive_buff_heroic = {
	if = {
		limit = {
			NOT = { has_country_flag = th_has_heroic_buff_active }
		}
		add_country_modifier = {
			name = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
			duration = -1
		}
		set_country_flag = th_has_heroic_buff_active
		#Placeholder for future effects
	}
	else_if = {
		limit = {
			has_country_modifier = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
		}
		remove_country_modifier = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
		add_country_modifier = {
			name = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_110
			duration = -1
		}

	}

add_th_diffuculty_passive_buff_heroic = {
	if = {
		limit = {
			NOT = { has_country_flag = th_has_heroic_buff_active }
		}
		add_country_modifier = {
			name = heroic_th_passive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
			duration = -1
		}
		set_country_flag = th_has_heroic_buff_active
		#Placeholder for future effects
	}
	else_if = {
		limit = {
			has_country_modifier = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_10000
		}
		remove_country_modifier = heroic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_10000
		#Placeholder for future effects
	}
	else_if = {
		limit = {
			has_country_modifier = heroic_th_passive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
		}
		remove_country_modifier = heroic_th_passive_ai_buff_against_dev_100

			name = heroic_th_passive_ai_buff_against_dev_200
			duration = -1
		}

add_th_diffuculty_buff_myhtic = {
	if = {
		limit = {
			NOT = { has_country_flag = th_has_mythic_buff_active }
		}
		add_country_modifier = {
			name = myhtic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
			duration = -1
		}
		set_country_flag = th_has_mythic_buff_active

	}
	else_if = {
		limit = {

add_th_diffuculty_buff_lunatic = {
	if = {
		limit = {
			NOT = { has_country_flag = th_has_lunatic_buff_active }
		}
		add_country_modifier = {
			name = lunatic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
			duration = -1
		}
		set_country_flag = th_has_lunatic_buff_active
		#Placeholder for future effects
	}
	else_if = {
		limit = {
			has_country_modifier = lunatic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
		}
		remove_country_modifier = lunatic_th_agressive_ai_buff_against_dev_100
